# 📊 Model Performance

Evaluation performed using historical test data.

Metrics:

- MAE
- RMSE
- R² Score


| Country | MAE (MW) | RMSE (MW) | R² |
|---|---:|---:|---:|
| Germany | 1138.73 | 1548.04 | 0.9718 |
| Greece | 134.79 | 197.35 | 0.9733 |
| Italy | 724.52 | 1147.23 | 0.9714 |
| France | 923.39 | 1329.29 | 0.9842 |
| Austria | 186.55 | 275.01 | 0.9563 |
| Netherlands | 265.96 | 369.76 | 0.9664 |

