# 🚀 Installation

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone <repository-url>

Create environment:

python -m venv venv

Activate:

Windows:

venv\Scripts\activate

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt
▶️ Run Forecast Dashboard

Start Streamlit:

streamlit run src/app.py
