💡 Key Takeaway

This project demonstrates an end-to-end energy analytics workflow:

Raw Data → Feature Engineering → Machine Learning → Forecast Engine → Business Dashboard

The objective is not only to build a predictive model, but to create a complete forecasting application that could support real-world electricity market analysis and operational decision-making.

